                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170917-97-off471 t18170917-97-cd472"></join>, four gowns, value 15s.; two shawls, value 2s., and one handkerchief, value 1s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18170917-97-victim663" type="victimName">
                        Soloman 
                        Soloman
                     <interp inst="t18170917-97-victim663" type="surname" value="Soloman"></interp>
